## Domain Modeli

### Hiyerarşi

```
CompanyGroup  →  Company  →  User
```

```
ADMIN > GROUP_MANAGER > ZONE_MANAGER > COMPANY_MANAGER > SUPERVISOR > STAFF
```

### Kritik Entity'ler

| Entity | Önemli Alanlar |
|--------|----------------|
| `CompanyGroupProductEntity` | `apiUrl`, `apiVersion`, `enabled`, `agreedUserCount`, `licenseExpiresAt`, `notes` |
| `UserProductEntity` | `product`, `applicationRole`, `departments`, `eulaAcceptedAt`, `lastSuccessLogin` |
| `UserEntity` | `username`, `password` (BCrypt), `passwordChangeRequired`, `passwordExpiresAt` |
| `Auditable` (base) | `id` (UUID), `createdBy`, `createdDate`, `lastModifiedBy`, `lastModifiedDate`, `version` |

